[25.944177, "o", "  Every monitor decision is appended to a hash-chained log. Each entry's\r\n  prev_hash binds to the previous entry's hash — tampering with any past\r\n  entry breaks the chain and verify_chain() detects it. That's the\r\n  FedRAMP-flavored integrity-evidence pattern this project is shaped\r\n  around.\r\n"]
